= Introduction to Music Production

==== What is Music Production?

Without becoming too philosophical, let us start with a brief description of what happens in music production and recording so that we know what we have to learn in order to prepare for creative work in the music industry. At some point MUTEBOOK might include some chapters on the history of recording, but there are great {online resources|link} already which you can study for now. Recording is a relatively young art (just over 100 years old), but technological developments have been introduced constantly and have changed the way music is created, recorded and produced. {add more here}

